lead_paragraph: - Ireland are under no illusions about the challenge that lies ahead as they prepare to face South Africa at Newlands on Saturday in the first of three tests, captain Rory Best said on the eve of the match.

headline.print_headline: Ireland Under No Illusions About South Africa Challenge
headline.main: Ireland Under No Illusions About South Africa Challenge
